# Project Rules for Arye Boutique

## Language
- The project is in Hebrew (RTL)
- Code comments can be in Hebrew or English
- User-facing text should be in Hebrew

## Tech Stack
- Django web framework
- HTML/CSS/JavaScript frontend
- SQLite database

## Code Style
- Use Hebrew variable names for user-facing content
- Follow Django best practices
- CSS follows BEM-like naming convention

## File Structure
- Templates in store/templates/store/
- Static files in static/css/ and static/js/
- Models in store/models.py

## Important Notes
- Site is RTL (right-to-left)
- Mobile-first responsive design
- All prices are in Israeli Shekels (ש"ח)

## Shell & Git
- Use PowerShell syntax for all shell commands (Windows environment)
- Do not use bash syntax like `&&` or heredocs
- For git commits use simple one-line messages: `git commit -m "message"`
- Working directory is: c:\arye-boutique